  "instructions": [
    "Heat a non-stick skillet over medium heat. Add ginger paste and minced garlic, stirring for about 30 seconds until fragrant.",
    "Add bell pepper and onion; stir-fry for another 1-2 minutes until vegetables begin to soften slightly.",
    "Push the vegetables aside in the pan, add zucchini slices and a pinch of salt, let cook for about 5 minutes. Stir occasionally.",
    "Distribute evenly over the veggies and toss with shredded coconut and sesame seeds. Add lime juice to taste, mix well.",
    "Serve hot immediately."
  ],
